==English==
/nuk/

===Noun===
#Nuclear weapon. 
#:"''I can buy '''nukes''' on the black market for $40 million each''" - John Travolta in the movie ''Swordfish''.
#Something that negates.

===Intransitive Verb===
#To negate. "The final exam ""nuked"" my chances for a good grade." 
#To use a nuclear weapon on a target.  ''First they '''nuked''' Hiroshima, then Nagasaki.''
#To cook food or beverages in a [[microwave oven]].  ''I'll '''nuke''' some pizza for dinner.''
#([[computing]]) to completely destroy a computer [[file]] or [[directory]]. ''To try to hide his posting history on [[Usenet]], he had his posts '''nuked''' from the [[Google]] archives.''

